      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are honored to present this vehicle in impeccable, showroom-grade condition. This specimen has been curated with the utmost attention to detail, manifesting a flawless aesthetic and mechanical profile that satisfies the most exacting standards. The interior remains in a state of absolute preservation, while the exterior finish retains its original luster, devoid of any imperfections. This is a premier opportunity to acquire a vehicle that transcends the standard used market, offering an experience indistinguishable from its original delivery. Serious inquiries are invited for a private viewing of this exceptional asset.",
