    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Offering a truly exceptional, collector-grade vehicle that presents in showroom condition. The exterior paint is flawless, retaining a deep factory luster with absolutely no stone chips, swirl marks, or blemishes. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, the original carpets are pristine, and every electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, this car is beyond reproach, supported by a comprehensive, specialized service history and recent fluid service. It has been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and driven only in fair weather. This is a rare opportunity to own a 'time capsule' example that looks, smells, and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. Includes all original keys, owner\u2019s manuals, and service records.",
      "price": 44800.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
